channel.title: Compiler Error
channel.description:
Note: If no one knows. That's fine. Because the server can still run with the error. I did look it up but couldn't find anything relevant to my issue
Hi, I'm kind of new to Private Server coding. So hear me out if this is a super easy problem to solve. I was using a tutorial to create a mystery box. I did everything it said. When I compiled I got, "src\server\model\players\packets\ClickItem.java:139: error: cannot find symbol c.getItems().addItem(arrayOfItems[Misc.random(arrayOfItems.length)], 1);
symbol: variable Misc location: class ClickItem
My 2 Guesses are that Misc isn't a variable or that I need to put the same code in the class file. If you can reply to me that'd be great :)
